  "keyFeatures": [
    "Auto task decomposition — describe a goal in plain text and the framework plans the task DAG automatically",
    "Parallel task execution with dependency-aware scheduling (topological sort)",
    "Model-agnostic — Claude, GPT, GitHub Copilot, Ollama, vLLM, LM Studio in the same team",
    "Three run modes: runAgent() for one-shot, runTeam() for auto-orchestration, runTasks() for explicit pipelines",
    "Coordinator pattern — built-in coordinator agent decomposes goals and synthesises final results",
    "Shared memory — agents read each other's outputs via a key-value MemoryStore",
    "Inter-agent messaging via MessageBus",
    "Concurrency control with AgentPool and Semaphore",
    "5 built-in tools: bash, file_read, file_write, file_edit, grep",
    "Custom tools via defineTool() with Zod schema validation"
  ],
